Report.Description: Invoiced turnover and quantity by finished product for the bill-to customer hierachy / Chiffre d'affaires et quantité facturés par article pour la hiérarchie du client facturé
Report.Author: Jerome DELORT

Query.CommandText:
select [ItemNum], [ItemDescFR], [ItemDescEN], [ItemDescIT], [ItemDescSP], [ItemDescPT], [ForecastItemNum], [ForecastItemDescFR], [ForecastItemDescEN], [ForecastItemDescIT], [ForecastItemDescSP], [ForecastItemDescPT], [CommercialVarietyCode], [CommercialVarietyDescFR], [CommercialVarietyDescEN], [CommercialVarietyDescIT], [CommercialVarietyDescSP], [CommercialVarietyDescPT], [SpeciesCode], [SpeciesDescFR], [SpeciesDescEN], [SpeciesDescIT], [SpeciesDescSP], [SpeciesDescPT], UnitMeasureForecastCode, [SalesUOM], [ItemUOM], [CompanyCurrencyCode], -- Turnover E-1 full exercise SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 THEN req.SalesValueInvoicedComp ELSE 0 END) as Turnover_Local_E_1, -- Quantity E-1 full exercise SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 THEN req.QtyInvoicedFCST ELSE 0 END) as QtyInvoicedFCST_Local_E_1, -- Turnover YTD-1 SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 AND req.DateToJoin<=DATEADD(year,-1,@P_Date) THEN req.SalesValueInvoicedComp ELSE 0 END) as Turnover_Local_YTD_1, -- Quantity YTD-1 SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 AND req.DateToJoin<=DATEADD(year,-1,@P_Date) THEN req.QtyInvoicedFCST ELSE 0 END) as QtyInvoicedFCST_Local_YTD_1, -- Turnover YTD SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam AND req.DateToJoin<=@P_Date THEN req.SalesValueInvoicedComp ELSE 0 END) as Turnover_Local_YTD, -- Quantity YTD SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam AND req.DateToJoin<=@P_Date THEN req.QtyInvoicedFCST ELSE 0 END) as QtyInvoicedFCST_Local_YTD, -- Turnover M-12 SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 AND req.PeriodLocal=req.PeriodLocalParam and req.DateToJoin<=DATEADD(year,-1,@P_Date) THEN req.SalesValueInvoicedComp ELSE 0 END) as Turnover_Local_M_12, -- Quantity M-12 SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 AND req.PeriodLocal=req.PeriodLocalParam and req.DateToJoin<=DATEADD(year,-1,@P_Date) THEN req.QtyInvoicedFCST ELSE 0 END) as QtyInvoicedFCST_Local_M_12, -- Turnover M SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam AND req.PeriodLocal=req.PeriodLocalParam and req.DateToJoin<=@P_Date THEN req.SalesValueInvoicedComp ELSE 0 END) as Turnover_Local_M, -- Quantity M SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam AND req.PeriodLocal=req.PeriodLocalParam and req.DateToJoin<=@P_Date THEN req.QtyInvoicedFCST ELSE 0 END) as QtyInvoicedFCST_Local_M, -- Open Turnover E full exercise SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam THEN req.SalesValueOpenInvoicedComp ELSE 0 END) as TurnoverOpen_Local_E, -- Quantity Open E full exercise SUM(CASE WHEN req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam THEN req.QtyOpenInvoicedFCST ELSE 0 END) as QtyOpenInvoicedFCST_Local_E, -- Open Turnover E-1 SUM(case when req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 and req.DateOrdered<>'1899-12-31 00:00:00.000' and req.DateOrdered<=DATEADD(YY,-1,@P_Date) and (req.DateInvoice >DATEADD(YY,-1,@P_Date) or req.DateInvoice='1899-12-31 00:00:00.000') and (req.DateCancelled >DATEADD(YY,-1,@P_Date) or req.DateCancelled='1899-12-31 00:00:00.000') then req.[SalesValueInvoicedComp] else 0 end) TurnoverOpen_Local_E_1 , -- Open Quantity E-1 SUM(case when req.FYLocal=req.FYLocalParam-1 and req.DateOrdered<>'1899-12-31 00:00:00.000' and req.DateOrdered<=DATEADD(YY,-1,@P_Date) and (req.DateInvoice >DATEADD(YY,-1,@P_Date) or req.DateInvoice='1899-12-31 00:00:00.000') and (req.DateCancelled >DATEADD(YY,-1,@P_Date) or req.DateCancelled='1899-12-31 00:00:00.000') then req.QtyInvoicedFCST else 0 end) QtyOpen_Local_E_1
from
( SELECT year(F_SalesOrders.[DateToJoin]) YearNum, month(F_SalesOrders.[DateToJoin]) MonthNum, F_SalesOrders.[DateToJoin], F_SalesOrders.DateOrdered, F_SalesOrders.DateActualShip, F_SalesOrders.DateCancelled, F_SalesOrders.DateInvoice, F_SalesOrders.FYLocal, F_SalesOrders.PeriodLocal, F_SalesOrders.[CompanyCode], Local_Exercice.FYLocalParam, Local_Exercice.PeriodLocalParam, (select per.FY from D_Period per where per.FYModel='O' and per.period not in (0,13,14) and @P_Date between per.StartPeriodDate and per.EndPeriodDate) as FYGroupParam, (select per.Period from D_Period per where per.FYModel='O' and per.period not in (0,13,14) and @P_Date between per.StartPeriodDate and per.EndPeriodDate) as PeriodGroupParam , [D_Item].[ItemNum], [D_Item].[ItemDescFR], [D_Item].[ItemDescEN], [D_Item].[ItemDescIT], [D_Item].[ItemDescSP], [D_Item].[ItemDescPT], [D_Item].[ForecastItemNum], [D_Item].[ForecastItemDescFR], [D_Item].[ForecastItemDescEN], [D_Item].[ForecastItemDescIT], [D_Item].[ForecastItemDescSP], [D_Item].[ForecastItemDescPT], [D_Item].[CommercialVarietyCode], [D_Item].[CommercialVarietyDescFR], [D_Item].[CommercialVarietyDescEN], [D_Item].[CommercialVarietyDescIT], [D_Item].[CommercialVarietyDescSP], [D_Item].[CommercialVarietyDescPT], [D_Item].[SpeciesCode], [D_Item].[SpeciesDescFR], [D_Item].[SpeciesDescEN], [D_Item].[SpeciesDescIT], [D_Item].[SpeciesDescSP], [D_Item].[SpeciesDescPT], F_SalesOrders.UnitMeasureForecastCode, F_SalesOrders.[QtyInvoicedFCST], F_SalesOrders.QtyOpenInvoicedFCST, F_SalesOrders.[SalesUOM], F_SalesOrders.[ItemUOM], F_SalesOrders.[SalesValueInvoicedComp], F_SalesOrders.SalesValueOpenInvoicedComp, F_SalesOrders.[CompanyCurrencyCode] FROM [dbo].[F_SalesOrders] inner join [dbo].[D_Item] on F_SalesOrders.[ItemNum]=[D_Item].[ItemNum] inner join [dbo].[D_Customer] on F_SalesOrders.[BillToCustNum]=[D_Customer].[CustNum] and F_SalesOrders.[CompanyCode]= [D_Customer].[CompanyCode] inner join (select D_FinancialCompany.CompanyCode, D_Period.FY FYLocalParam, D_Period.Period PeriodLocalParam from D_FinancialCompany inner join D_Period on D_FinancialCompany.FYModel=D_Period.FYModel and @P_Date between D_Period.StartPeriodDate and D_Period.EndPeriodDate where D_Period.Period not in (0,13,14)) Local_Exercice On Local_Exercice.CompanyCode=F_SalesOrders.CompanyCode where F_SalesOrders.DateToJoin BETWEEN DATEADD(year,-2,@P_Date) AND DATEADD(year,1,@P_Date) and [F_SalesOrders].CompanyCode in (@P_Company)
and [D_Customer].HubCode in (@P_Hub) and [D_Customer].SalesRepLevelCode in (@P_SalesRepLevel) and [D_Customer].BUSalesRegionCode in (@P_SalesRegion) and [D_Customer].BUSalesAreaCode in (@P_SalesArea) and [D_Customer].SalesRepBuyerCode in (@P_SalesRep)
and [D_Item].ProductTypeCode='PFI' and [D_Item].SpeciesCode in (@P_Species)
) req group by [ItemNum], [ItemDescFR], [ItemDescEN], [ItemDescIT], [ItemDescSP], [ItemDescPT], [ForecastItemNum], [ForecastItemDescFR], [ForecastItemDescEN], [ForecastItemDescIT], [ForecastItemDescSP], [ForecastItemDescPT], [CommercialVarietyCode], [CommercialVarietyDescFR], [CommercialVarietyDescEN], [CommercialVarietyDescIT], [CommercialVarietyDescSP], [CommercialVarietyDescPT], [SpeciesCode], [SpeciesDescFR], [SpeciesDescEN], [SpeciesDescIT], [SpeciesDescSP], [SpeciesDescPT], UnitMeasureForecastCode, [SalesUOM], [ItemUOM], [CompanyCurrencyCode]

select D_FinancialCompany.CompanyCode, D_FinancialCompany.CompanyDesc from dbo.D_FinancialCompany inner join ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecurityCompany on AdmSecurityCompany.companycode=D_FinancialCompany.companycode where AdmSecurityCompany.UserDomainLogin=@P_User Order BY D_FinancialCompany.CompanyDesc

="SELECT " + " (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 88) as LblReportTitle " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 60) as LblParameters " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 89) as LblUser " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 59) as LblDate " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 14) as LblCompany " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 23) as LblHub " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 24) as LblSalesRepLevel " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 25) as LblSalesRegion " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 70) as LblSalesArea " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 32) as LblSalesRep " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 38) as LblSpecies " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 5) as LblMonth " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 77) as LblYTD " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 90) as LblQtyInvoiced " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 85) as LblTurnover " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 133) as LblOpenOrders " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 172) as LblAvgSalPrice " + ", (SELECT " + Parameters!P_Language.Value + " FROM AdmTranslation WHERE CounterID = 58) as LblExecutionTime "
SELECT distinct ModelType FROM D_FinancialCompany WHERE ModelType ='Group'

SELECT distinct D_Customer.SalesRepBuyerCode, D_Customer.SalesRepBuyerName FROM D_Customer INNER JOIN ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecuritySalesRepBuyer ON AdmSecuritySalesRepBuyer.SalesRepBuyerCode = D_Customer.SalesRepBuyerCode WHERE D_Customer.BUSalesAreaCode in(@P_SalesArea)and D_Customer.SalesRepBuyerCode not like '>%' and AdmSecuritySalesRepBuyer.UserDomainLogin = @P_User ORDER BY D_Customer.SalesRepBuyerName

SELECT distinct D_Customer.BUSalesAreaCode,D_Customer.BUSalesAreaDesc FROM D_Customer INNER JOIN ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecurityBUSalesArea ON AdmSecurityBUSalesArea.BUSalesAreaCode = D_Customer.BUSalesAreaCode WHERE BUSalesRegionCode in(@P_SalesRegion) and AdmSecurityBUSalesArea.UserDomainLogin = @P_User ORDER BY D_Customer.BUSalesAreaDesc ASC

SELECT DISTINCT D_Customer.HubCode, D_Customer.HubName FROM D_Customer INNER JOIN ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecurityHub ON AdmSecurityHub.HubCode = D_Customer.HubCode WHERE (AdmSecurityHub.UserDomainLogin = @P_User) AND (D_Customer.HubCode <> '') and D_Customer.CompanyCode in (@P_Company) ORDER BY D_Customer.HubName

SELECT DISTINCT D_Customer.SalesRepLevelCode, D_Customer.SalesRepLevelName FROM D_Customer INNER JOIN ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecuritySalesRepLevel ON AdmSecuritySalesRepLevel.SalesRepLevelCode = D_Customer.SalesRepLevelCode WHERE (D_Customer.SalesRepLevelCode IS NOT NULL) AND (D_Customer.SalesRepLevelCode NOT LIKE '>%') AND (AdmSecuritySalesRepLevel.UserDomainLogin = @P_User) and D_Customer.HubCode in(@P_Hub) ORDER BY D_Customer.SalesRepLevelName asc

SELECT DISTINCT D_Customer.BUSalesRegionCode, D_Customer.BUSalesRegionName FROM D_Customer INNER JOIN ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecurityBUSalesRegion ON ADM_BI.dbo.AdmSecurityBUSalesRegion.BUSalesRegionCode = D_Customer.BUSalesRegionCode WHERE (D_Customer.BUSalesRegionCode IS NOT NULL) and D_Customer.SalesRepLevelCode in(@P_SalesRepLevel) and AdmSecurityBUSalesRegion.UserDomainLogin = @P_User ORDER BY D_Customer.BUSalesRegionName asc

="SELECT distinct [SpeciesCode],[SpeciesDesc" + Parameters!P_Language.Value + "] as [SpeciesDesc] FROM [dbo].[D_Item] where [D_Item].ProductTypeCode='PFI' and SpeciesCode not like '>%' order by [SpeciesDesc] asc"

Report.Code:
Public Function EvolutionRate(ByVal a as String, ByVal b as String) As Decimal If IsNothing(b) or IsNothing(a) or IsDBNull(a) or IsDBNull(b) or a = "" or b = "" Then EvolutionRate = Nothing ElseIf b = 0 Then EvolutionRate = 0 Else EvolutionRate = (CDec(a) / CDec(b)) - 1 End If return EvolutionRate End function
Public Function Division(ByVal a as String, ByVal b as String) As Decimal If IsNothing(b) or IsNothing(a) or IsDBNull(a) or IsDBNull(b) or a = "" or b = "" Then Division = Nothing ElseIf b = 0 Then Division = 0 Else Division = (CDec(a) / CDec(b)) End If return Division End function
Public Function Dec(ByVal a as String) As Decimal If IsNothing(a) or IsDBNull(a) or a = "" Then Dec = Nothing Else Dec = CDec(a) End If return Dec End function
